snippet.title: AX-5 for the NEC PC-6001 mkII
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

AX-5 is a compilation consisting of two games with 2 different graphic modes (one in colour and one in black and white).

Olion: A first-person space shooter. Shoot the alien ships, but avoid their shots. You also have limited fuel.
The controls in this game are reversed.

Quest - The Adventure: A first-person maze game where you have to hunt and kill the alien and collect the key it drops, then you have to find the exit. You have to hurry as you have limited oxygen and also limited ammo. However, there are red items that are either oxygen pills or ammo.
